📚 This repository contains a collection of beginner-friendly Python programs. 
The projects include ➕ adding two user-input numbers, 🐾 responding to the user's favorite animal, 
🌡️ converting temperatures from Fahrenheit to Celsius, 👥 solving an age-related riddle by calculating the ages of friends, 
📐 computing the perimeter of a triangle based on user input, and 🔢 finding the square of a number. 
Each program demonstrates basic Python concepts like variables, user input, type conversion, arithmetic operations, and formatted output. 🐍✨
